                            jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                            sling:resourceType="menarinimaster/components/text"
                            text="&lt;table align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;width: 458px;&quot;>&#xa;    &lt;tbody>&#xa;        &lt;tr>&#xa;            &lt;td>&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/logo_M_cs.jpg&quot; />&lt;/td>&#xa;            &lt;td>&amp;nbsp;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/DynamoCamp/logo-Dynamo-web.jpg&quot; style=&quot;float: right;&quot; />&lt;/td>&#xa;        &lt;/tr>&#xa;    &lt;/tbody>&#xa;&lt;/table>&#xa;&lt;br />&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&#xa;&lt;strong>&lt;span>Florence, July 12, 2017&lt;/span>&lt;/strong>&lt;span>: Employee training in the name of solidarity:  today a group of Menarini pharma employees took part in a training exercise by preparing 15,000 meals for countries currently in seriously critical situations.&#xa;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&#xa;&lt;span>This initiative is the fruit of a successful collaboration with the association &lt;em>Stop Hunger Now&lt;/em>(Rise Against Hunger), a non-profit organization with the purpose of providing a tangible contribution to the fight against world hunger and to supporting children&amp;rsquo;s rights, with &lt;em>Dynamo Academy&lt;/em>, a social enterprise that focusses on training in the context of social entrepreneurship, and with &lt;em>, &lt;/em>a company specializing in human resource evaluation and development.&lt;/span>&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&#xa;&lt;span>The training location was at the Tuscan campus of Dynamo Academy in Limestre (Pistoia).&lt;/span>&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;font-style: italic; text-align: center;&quot;>&#xa;&lt;span>&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/Portals/31/Images/notizie/DynamoCamp/Dipendenti-Menarini-alla-Dynamo-Academy_web.jpg&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot; />&lt;/span>&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&#xa;&lt;span>A team of Menarini employees were busy for a full day putting together 15,000 meals that will allow one of the communities assisted by the association in Zimbabwe to host 50 new children for a full school year.  Today's course was focused on developing and improving various skills such as organizational effectiveness, teamwork, problem solving and negotiation among colleagues, in addition to adaptability in a new context that is different from the usual setting of a familiar business office.  Also of great value is the initiative&amp;rsquo;s social contribution which will allow children, faced with the daily difficulty of nourishing themselves, to receive a supply of meals for themselves and their families.  Today was &quot;good for the heart&quot; of those who prepared meals and of those who will receive them.&lt;/span>&#xa;&lt;/p>&#xa;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;>&#xa;&lt;span>The Menarini employee team was engaged in a context that metaphorically represented a complex company where planning carefully, working with high-quality standards and distributing on a capillary level are activities for which it is strategic and essential to work together and effectively communicate among colleagues.  All for one and one for all.&lt;/span>&#xa;&lt;/p>"
                            textIsRich="true"/>
